PRISONAM FRANGENTIBOUS, STAT- UTE DE. The English statute 1 Kdw. II. St. 2, (in Rev. St. 23 Edw. I.,) a still unrepealed statute, whereby it is felony for a felon to break prison, but misdemeanor only for a misdemeanant to do so. 1 Hale, P.G 612.
